To install, you'll need the following dependencies to be able to use Socrata APIs:

1. python2
2. Python pandas library - run "pip install pandas"
3. Python sodapy library - run "pip install sodapy"

To run: 
python2 show-open-food-trucks.py 

Notes:
I tested on python version :
Python 2.7.16 and ran on a Macbook Pro.